# AsFix Deploy Rules

Follow `DEPLOY.md` for Render/Vercel steps.

## Production env
```
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=5000
CORS_ORIGIN=https://your-domain.com
```

## Build commands
- Full install: `npm run install:all`
- Seed (first run): `npm run seed`
- Dev: `npm run dev` (frontend :5173 + backend :5000)
- Prod: `npm run start:prod` or Render start command from DEPLOY.md

## Before deploy
1. Run `npm run build --prefix frontend` — must pass
2. Update shop address/phone in `frontend/src/config/shop.js`
3. Set `CORS_ORIGIN` to live domain
4. Run `npm run reset-admin` locally if default password was used

## Domain (budget)
- Free start: `*.onrender.com`
- Pakistan: `asfixgear.com.pk` (~Rs 2–3.5k/yr)
- International: `asfixgear.com` (~$10–12/yr)
- Point DNS CNAME to Render custom domain; SSL is automatic

## Do not
- Force push to main
- Commit `.env` or `backend/data/data.json`
- Deploy without setting production CORS when frontend is on a different origin
